title: #92Noon Live from TCO! Lombardi/Krawczynski/Amundson/Urban
description: #92Noon is back LIVE from the TCO Performance Center! Michael Lombardi from The Athletic calls in to talk about the NFL. Plus, live coverage of the Mike Zimmer weekly presser. Cy Amundson stops by to share what he does for ESPN's Snapchat. Darren Urban calls in to talk about the Arizona Cardinals, and Jon Krawczynski joins the show to talk about the latest in the Jimmy Butler controversy.
